    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼警告特朗普“想打破我们”，加拿大高风险开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/carney-warns-trump-wants-to-break-us-as-high-stakes-canadian-election-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）开始竞标选举，并警告说，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认真对待想要吞并加拿大的努力，以说服加拿大人他可以保护该国免受美国侵略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/carney-warns-trump-wants-to-break-us-as-high-stakes-canadian-election-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 02:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
